## ERROR MESSAGES TO USE (Consistent UX)
```
camera denied   → "Camera access blocked. Go to browser Settings → allow camera → refresh"
no food found   → "No food detected. Move closer and ensure good lighting"
api timeout     → "AI is taking too long. Please try again"
auth expired    → "Session expired. Please login again"
network error   → "No internet connection. Check your WiFi"
scan failed     → "Scan failed: [actual error]. Try uploading a photo instead"
```

